@startuml
participant "Worfklow Runner - Worker" as Prefect
participant "folio API" as External
participant "folio Queue Processor (Celery)" as Celery
participant "Workflow Runner - API" as PrefectAPI

== Flow Execution Starts ==
Prefect -> External: Start Long-running Task (POST /process {task_id: PREFECT_TASK_ID})
External -> Celery: Queue Task with prefect callback 
External -> Prefect: {job_id: 123, ...}
Prefect -> Prefect: PREFECT_PAUSE()

== External Task Processing ==
Celery -> Celery: Process Long-running Task


== Celery Notifies Prefect ==
Celery -> PrefectAPI: POST f"{PREFECT_API_URL}{task_run_id}/set_state" COMPLETED
PrefectAPI -> Prefect: Resume Flow (resume_flow_run)

== Prefect Continues Execution ==
Prefect -> Prefect: Resume and Run Dependent Task
Prefect -> PrefectAPI: Task Marked as COMPLETED

@enduml
